      Guidance
    </span>
  <h1 class="gem-c-title__text gem-c-title__text--long">
    Face coverings in education
  </h1>
</div>
  </div>
  

  <div class="govuk-grid-column-two-thirds">
    
  <p class="gem-c-lead-paragraph">Guidance on the use of face coverings for schools and other education institutions that teach people in years 7 and above in England.</p>

  </div>
</div>

